---
---

<section class="section platform-section" id="platforms">
	<div class="container">
		<div class="eyebrow">PLATFORMS //</div>
		<h2 class="section-title">Hardware appliance or software install — your call.</h2>
		<p class="section-lede">
			PicoCluster Claw hardware is the flagship: plug in, power on, agents running
			in minutes. But the full OpenClaw + ThreadWeaver stack installs on Mac,
			Linux, and Windows too — same experience, your existing machine.
		</p>

		<div class="platform-grid">
			<div class="platform platform-featured">
				<div class="platform-badge">FLAGSHIP</div>
				<div class="platform-icon">🖥</div>
				<h3>PicoCluster Claw</h3>
				<p class="platform-desc">
					The two-node cluster appliance. ClusterClaw runs OpenClaw agents.
					ClusterCrush handles local LLM inference via Ollama + CUDA.
					Ships pre-installed and pre-configured — no assembly required.
				</p>
				<ul class="check-list">
					<li>OpenClaw pre-installed</li>
					<li>ThreadWeaver chat interface</li>
					<li>28 MCP tools built-in</li>
					<li>LED strip feedback</li>
					<li>Dedicated inference silicon</li>
					<li>Always-on, 14W idle</li>
				</ul>
				<a class="btn btn-primary" href="https://picocluster.com" rel="noopener">
					Order now →
				</a>
			</div>

			<div class="platform-software">
				<div class="sw-card">
					<div class="sw-icon">🍎</div>
					<div class="sw-body">
						<h3>macOS</h3>
						<p>
							Docker Compose overlay for Apple Silicon and Intel Macs.
							ThreadWeaver + OpenClaw on your laptop.
							Install with one command.
						</p>
						<a class="sw-link" href="/getting-started/quickstart/">macOS install →</a>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="sw-card">
					<div class="sw-icon">🐧</div>
					<div class="sw-body">
						<h3>Linux</h3>
						<p>
							Native install or Docker Compose. Full MCP tool support,
							Ollama integration, ThreadWeaver chat — identical to
							the hardware experience.
						</p>
						<a class="sw-link" href="/getting-started/quickstart/">Linux install →</a>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="sw-card">
					<div class="sw-icon">🪟</div>
					<div class="sw-body">
						<h3>Windows</h3>
						<p>
							WSL2 + Docker Compose overlay. Run OpenClaw and
							ThreadWeaver from Windows Terminal — same stack,
							same agents.
						</p>
						<a class="sw-link" href="/getting-started/quickstart/">Windows install →</a>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="sw-note">
					Software paths use the same Docker Compose base with
					platform-specific overlays — one codebase, three targets.
					Upgrade with a single <code>git pull</code>.
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.platform-section {
		background:
			radial-gradient(
				ellipse 50% 50% at 0% 50%,
				rgba(27, 117, 186, 0.05),
				transparent 60%
			),
			var(--ctx-bg);
	}

	.eyebrow {
		display: inline-block;
		padding: 0.3rem 0.8rem;
		background: rgba(27, 117, 186, 0.08);
		border: 1px solid rgba(27, 117, 186, 0.28);
		border-radius: 999px;
		font-family: var(--ctx-font-mono);
		font-size: 0.68rem;
		letter-spacing: 0.1em;
		color: var(--claw-blue-text);
		font-weight: 700;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
	}

	.platform-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.4fr;
		gap: 1.5rem;
		margin-top: 0.5rem;
		align-items: start;
	}

	.platform-featured {
		background: var(--ctx-panel);
		border: 1px solid rgba(27, 117, 186, 0.4);
		border-radius: var(--ctx-radius-lg);
		padding: 2rem;
		position: relative;
	}

	.platform-badge {
		position: absolute;
		top: 1rem;
		right: 1rem;
		padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem;
		background: rgba(27, 117, 186, 0.15);
		border: 1px solid rgba(27, 117, 186, 0.4);
		border-radius: 999px;
		font-family: var(--ctx-font-mono);
		font-size: 0.62rem;
		letter-spacing: 0.1em;
		color: var(--claw-blue-text);
		font-weight: 700;
	}

	.platform-icon {
		font-size: 2rem;
		margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
	}

	.platform-featured h3 {
		font-size: 1.3rem;
		font-weight: 800;
		color: #ffffff;
		margin: 0 0 0.75rem 0;
	}

	.platform-desc {
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		color: var(--ctx-text-dim);
		margin: 0 0 1.25rem 0;
		line-height: 1.55;
	}

	.check-list {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
		margin: 0 0 1.5rem 0;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 0.45rem;
	}

	.check-list li {
		font-size: 0.88rem;
		color: var(--ctx-text-dim);
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 0.5rem;
	}

	.check-list li::before {
		content: '✓';
		color: var(--claw-blue-text);
		font-weight: 700;
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		flex-shrink: 0;
	}

	.platform-software {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 1rem;
	}

	.sw-card {
		display: flex;
		gap: 1rem;
		background: var(--ctx-panel);
		border: 1px solid var(--ctx-border);
		border-radius: var(--ctx-radius-lg);
		padding: 1.25rem;
		align-items: flex-start;
	}

	.sw-icon {
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		flex-shrink: 0;
		width: 2.25rem;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.sw-body h3 {
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: #ffffff;
		margin: 0 0 0.35rem 0;
	}

	.sw-body p {
		font-size: 0.85rem;
		color: var(--ctx-text-dim);
		margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
		line-height: 1.5;
	}

	.sw-link {
		font-size: 0.82rem;
		color: var(--claw-blue-text);
		font-weight: 600;
	}

	.sw-link:hover {
		color: #ffffff;
	}

	.sw-note {
		font-size: 0.82rem;
		color: var(--ctx-text-faint);
		padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
		background: var(--ctx-panel);
		border: 1px dashed var(--ctx-border);
		border-radius: var(--ctx-radius-md);
		line-height: 1.5;
	}

	.sw-note code {
		background: var(--ctx-panel-hi);
		border: 1px solid var(--ctx-border-hi);
		padding: 0.1rem 0.35rem;
		border-radius: var(--ctx-radius-sm);
		font-family: var(--ctx-font-mono);
		font-size: 0.9em;
		color: var(--claw-blue-text);
	}

	@media (max-width: 800px) {
		.platform-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
	}
</style>
